N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5611.2 - Approval required

State Regulations

No registrant shall consummate any transaction, including
a material debt transaction, that would preclude such registrant's ability to
meet the requirements set forth in section
5611.1
of this Part, without prior
written approval by the commission. Notes
